{% if PromptLanguage == "en" %}
Based on the chapter, update {{ CharacterName }}'s visual profile to reflect how they appear in this chapter.

Output a JSON object with these fields:
- `visual_prompt`: Updated AI image generation prompt (English). Must follow the 12-dimension format:
  gender tag (1girl/1boy/etc.), age appearance, hair (color+style+length), eyes (color+shape), face shape, skin tone,
  body build, outfit (all clothing+accessories described in detail), current emotional expression,
  any chapter-specific details (wounds, special items, altered appearance),
  art style tokens (anime/realistic/etc.), quality tokens (masterpiece, best quality, etc.)
  Minimum 80 words. If nothing changed from the current profile, keep it mostly the same but ensure completeness.
- `description`: Updated character description in English (2-3 sentences covering personality, role, and current chapter context). Max 200 words.

Output ONLY valid JSON — no markdown fences, no explanation.
Example:
{"visual_prompt": "1girl, ...", "description": "..."}
